import datetime

def get_day_of_week_utc_unix(ts: int) -> str:
    utc_time = datetime.datetime.utcfromtimestamp(ts)
    days_of_week = ['', 'Tuesday', 'Wednesday', 'Thursday', 'Friday', 'Saturday', 'Sunday']
    return days_of_week[utc_time.weekday()]
